spanGrp.span: da gidabalool an qawasch gidayiiny gab gisireed
Me, I will speak, I am Gidayiiny of Gisireeda
Mimi nitaongea mimi ni Gidayiiny wa Gisireda
ha anin gidabalool anin gand mtal
I will speak, I am in Matala
I am a person of Matala
I grew up in this land
aa heed qay ayiinyay lapu gwarug qay hees
And the place I heard that the elders came from in the old days
Na nilikosikia mahali walikotoka wazee wakubwa wa zamani
qay gwalab gayeewajeeg eed sigur eernyot
They came from a place called Ernyota
They were driven out by other tribes
gahoonu eemoojiiga gehoonan ernyot aa gaway aa gaway garratu
They were driven out by other tribes and went until Karatu
walifukuzwa na makabila mengine wakaenda mpaka karatu
aa much gwarg aa gehoon aa qofk mang'ola
Later they came and were driven out until Mang'ola
siku nyimgine wakaja wakafukuzwa mpaka mang´ola
qang'ad qanyingees hana gwand mang' ol gobiideew mang'l
When I grew up there was Mang'ola, they lived in Mang'ola
Nilipopata fahamu yupo mang´ola anakaa mang´ola
asaha qawuny da daa gidab gewasch asimjeega
I came to recognize that we are Asimjeeg
Nikaja kutambua kwamba sisi ni waasimjeega
aa gewasch eemed sisitii qwasidees eemojig
When we were tribes that hated each other, we were hated by the tribes
Tukiwa makabila ambao wanachukiwa, tunachukiwa na makabila
asees ar welweld ar iwelwel gewasch ee fug ee nyiiseen gebus ab naweed aa gebar qameew
We, even to walk, if we went walking we were killed right there in the road
Sisi hata kutembea tukitembea tunauawa hukohuko barabarani
gebar qameew ab gidab ewoney ind qanya asimjand gili
And the person will be killed just for being seen, because they are Asimjeeg
Na atauawa kwa kuonewa tu kwa sababu ni mwasimjeega tu
And you will be killed by a Darorajeega
gawudeeny aa manal gisiway esinsaj aboshu gey nyiis geway eshimeew haweg sid
He shoots you with an arrow and then you don't know what they are going to do, I hear often they went to sing their praises to girls
Anakupiga na mshale na sijui wanaenda kufanya nini nasikia huwa wanaenda kujisifia kwa wasichana
eed qay aday aa qang'ad qanyingeesu qawuny da daa ng'ashanj
This is what I saw in the old days, and it makes me see that problem again
Ndicho nilichoona zamani na ikanirudia kuona tena lile jambo
aa eed qay bay qang'eedeew qay qang'eedeew someeg aa gosungukaad gaway aa gaway qwalap dita
And where the Asimjeeg came from in the old days, they came from Someega and went around, they went to pass by there
Na walikotoka zamani waasimjeega walitokea Someega na wakazunguka wakaaenda wakaenda kupitia huko
aa gaway ha qwalap gidbeeshiit aa gaway eernyooti
They passed by Gidabeshiita, they went until Ernyota
aa gegudgut aa efk eragw gicha
They were sent far and were returned east again
Wakapelekwa mpaka mbali na kurudishwa tena mashariki
aa qamn qwayiid ar mtal surj qwayiid mtal
Until they reached Matala, others had reached Matala
Mpaka wakafika matal wengine wamefiks matala
as ha imuch anin ija dadaa gidab qanee buneed qan aa munyas buneed gwasidaday geyeet
And me, I realized that there are bad people, and people hate each other
Na mimi kama nitakundua kuwa watu ni wabaya watu wanachukiana
qawasch qareemaneed aa lugweeg aagaweenj ga sang'a
I was a boy and I went to the youth groups a lot
Nilikuwa kijana na katika vikundi nimeenda vingi
aa gaweej da siy geng'uch aa basuguma
And I went and the ones who were fighting were the Sukuma
I saw a person who was killed
I saw a person who was beaten until he died
manung' darang' anin am siqus gidab qaday sii sibar
Me, I haven't killed a person, but I saw someone who was killed
Mimi sijamua mtu lakini kuona aliyeuawa
as ha ar ab dabaqeeg aa geng'ucheweja
Even the Maasai, they were warring with us a lot
The problems which we often face are these
Matatizo ambao huwa tunakutana nayo ni hayo
ar qamn aa mandan ar gid ng'wana
gid ng'wan gija naha ar qamn gayeeny qaweedees aseet gichay aa asees gadeegudgutanees
What would rest be like? Even now I say it is only God who is helping us, and we are still struggling
Unafuu itakuwa ni nini hata sasa nasema ni mungu tu anatusaidia na bado tunapambana
And we are deceived a lot
We are deceived and played, even now
gendij aa mandana eed sigur ee
We are here and there is no place called
Tupo hapo na hakuna mahali panaitwa
gey ng'anyiid gequs gobal eemoojig gichay
They say the land will be administered by just the tribes
Wanasema nchi itatawaliwa na makabila tu
iigal hij aa basukumajanda gigal hija aa daroorajanda
If you go here it's Sukuma and if you go there it's Darorajeega
Ukienda huku ni wasukuma na ukienda huko ni wadarorajeeg
ha gid qay qaday aa nihi
What I know of the old days is this
anin gid qay qaday aa nihi ab ng'anyiin
What I saw in the old days is this, in this land
Mimi nilichoona zamani ni hiki katika nchi hii
aa gagul qamn daheed qamn qawuuy gwalanyanda
Until now, I'm older, now I've become an elder
Mpaka sasa niwa mkubwa mimi sasa nimekuwa mzee
aa ng'asheeg qamn aa gitobiiw mandan
And there aren't any problems that have been resolved
ar qamn gayeeny qwadobiw aa geequs gidab aseet gil qaweedees aseet gichay
Even now I saw it's become good but it is only God who is helping us
Hata sasa nasema yamekuwa mazuri lakini ni mungu tu anatusaidia
Us, it's only God who is helping us
If I repeat these, what would it add?
